window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Earthquakes? Or poltergeists?</b></p> <p><b>The second installment in the popular </b><b><i>Ghostsitter </i></b><b>series.</b></p> <p>Tom's life changed quite a bit since he inherited a Ghost Train full of living dead creatures. As the fairground is struck by mysterious earthquakes, even Mimi the ghost-girl seems to pale. Vlarad the Vampire has reason to believe that a restless poltergeist haunts the old town square. So, Tom and his undead friends have to go ghost-hunting - without anyone noticing, of course.</p> <p>The second adventure of 14-year-old Tom and his ghostly companions is full of spooks, gags and some surprises - a joy for listeners young, old, and undead alike.</p> <p>Now available in Dolby Atmos on Audible.</p>"; 
